{"tid":2365211,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大家小心！開始有淡友全面進攻  short ARKK ！","createTime":"2021-01-13T14:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T18:26:19.000Z","uid":118346,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"f5aa5ebc2247ff7e44cc16695c03f497d1c9c40d","tid":2365211,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:23:40.000Z","msg":"Bearish Bets Against Ark ETFs Surge After &lsquo;Meteoric&rsquo; Rally<br />\n<br />\nA cohort of contrarians are wagering that the torrid streak for the top three exchange-traded funds managed by Cathie Wood will soon fizzle out.<br />\n<br />\nShort interest as a percentage of shares outstanding on the flagship $21 billion ARK Innovation ETF (ticker ARKK) jumped to an all-time high of 1.9% from about 0.3% a month ago, according to data from IHS Markit Ltd. A similar spike can be seen across the Ark Investment Management lineup, with bearish wagers on the $9.4 billion ARK Genomic Revolution ETF (ticker ARKG) and the $5.9 billion ARK Next Generation Internet ETF (ticker ARKW) also near records.<br />\n<br />\n淡友全面進攻！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033e49c9a75989ce99da8f48df4fa52245f79ece","tid":2365211,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d658b3215f098e98430b3229d8d5b0c17b6728","tid":2365211,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:35:15.000Z","msg":"走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3641fab35aebdcf2a0e62b60a61a70a87bafd53","tid":2365211,"uid":108266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:36:25.000Z","msg":"short